qcuts = pd.cut(d['Area'], bins=[1,2, 5, 10, 25, 50, 100, 250, 1000, 10000], precision=0)
fig, ax = plt.subplots(layout='constrained', dpi=200)
sns.boxplot(data=d, x=qcuts, y='hf', hue='hf_method', ax=ax)
ax.set_xticklabels(ax.get_xticklabels(), rotation=30)
(
    so.Plot(x=qcuts.cat.categories, y=0, text=[f"{item:.0f}" for item in qcuts.value_counts().values/2])
    .add(so.Text(fontsize='xx-small',valign='top', offset=5))
    .on(ax)
    .plot()
)
ax.grid(which='both', axis='y')
ax.yaxis.set_major_locator(mpl.ticker.MultipleLocator(100))
ax.set_xlabel('Area (km2)')
ax.set_ylabel('Thickness (m)')
ax.set_title('Below-ELA Thickness')

lonW = -170
lonE = -129
latS = 53
latN = 71
cLat = (latN + latS) / 2
cLon = (lonW + lonE) / 2
res = '50m'

plot_title = "Median difference, (Millan - Farinotti)"
filename = "hfDiff_tau"

# plot_title = "Median difference, (Millan < Farinotti)"
# filename = "hfDiff_less"
# diff = diff.loc[diff['diff'] <= 0]

# plot_title = "Median difference, (Millan > Farinotti)"
# filename = "hfDiff_more"
# diff = diff.loc[diff['diff'] > 0]

# plot_title = "Median difference 0 - 25 km2, (Millan - Farinotti)"
# filename = "hfDiff_0-25km2"
# diff = diff.loc[diff['Area'] <= 25]

# plot_title = "Median difference > 25 km2, (Millan - Farinotti)"
# filename = "hfDiff_gt25km2"
# diff = diff.loc[diff['Area'] > 25]

diff = gd_m.rgi.merge(gd_f.rgi.loc[:, ['RGIId', 'hf', 'tau', 'bt']], on='RGIId', suffixes=['_millan', '_farinotti'])
diff['diff'] = diff['hf_millan'] - diff['hf_farinotti']
diff['diff_tau'] = diff['tau_millan'] - diff['tau_farinotti']

plot_titles = [
    "Median difference, (Millan - Farinotti)",
    "Median difference, (Millan < Farinotti)",
    "Median difference, (Millan > Farinotti)",
    "Median difference 0 - 25 km2, (Millan - Farinotti)",
    "Median difference > 25 km2, (Millan - Farinotti)"
]
filenames = [
    "hfDiff"
    "hfDiff_less",
    "hfDiff_more",
    "hfDiff_0-25km2",
    "hfDiff_gt25km2",
]
diff_masks = [
    [True]*len(diff), 
    diff['diff'] > 0,
    diff['diff'] < 0,
    diff["Area"] <= 25,
    diff["Area"] > 25,
]

for plot_title, filename, diff_mask in zip(plot_titles, filenames, diff_masks):

    difff = diff[diff_mask].copy()
    
    fig = plt.figure(figsize=(3.5, 2.25), dpi=300, layout='constrained')
    gs = mpl.gridspec.GridSpec(3, 2, height_ratios=(1, 1, 1), figure=fig)
    mapax = fig.add_subplot(gs[0:3, :], projection=ccrs.LambertConformal(central_longitude=cLon, central_latitude=cLat))
    
    
    
    
    ######################
    # Map
    ######################
    mapax.set_extent([lonW, lonE, latS, latN], crs=ccrs.PlateCarree())
    mapax.set_aspect('auto', adjustable=None)
    coast = cfeature.NaturalEarthFeature(
        category='physical',
        name='coastline',
        scale=res,
        facecolor='none')
    borders = cfeature.NaturalEarthFeature(
        category='cultural',
        name='admin_0_boundary_lines_land',
        scale=res,
        facecolor='none')
    mapax.add_feature(borders, linewidth=0.25, edgecolor='black', alpha=0.5)
    mapax.add_feature(coast, linewidth=0.25, edgecolor='black', alpha=0.5)
    
    hex = mapax.hexbin(
        difff.CenLon,
        difff.CenLat,
        C=difff['diff_tau'],
        gridsize=(50, 15),
        #bins='log',
        transform=ccrs.PlateCarree(),
        reduce_C_function=np.median,
        visible=False,
    )
    offsets = hex.get_offsets()
    values = hex.get_array()
    vmin, vmax = values.min(), values.max()
    vmag = np.maximum(np.abs(vmin), np.abs(vmax))
    #norm = mpl.colors.CenteredNorm(vcenter=0)
    norm = mpl.colors.AsinhNorm(linear_width=10, vmin=-vmag, vmax=vmag)
    scat = mapax.scatter(
        offsets[:,0],
        offsets[:,1],
        c=values,
        norm=norm,
        s=4,
        cmap='PiYG',
    )
    
    
    cmap = plt.get_cmap('RdBu')
    #colors = cmap(np.linspace(0, 1, 12))
    nticks = 10
    
    #tick_values = norm(tick_labels)
    #bounds = np.linspace(0, 1, nticks+1)[:-1]  # even spacing
    transformed_bounds = np.linspace(-vmag, vmag, nticks)
    transformed_bounds = norm(transformed_bounds)
    
    steps = np.linspace(0, 1, nticks)
    color_bounds = norm.inverse(steps)
    diffs = np.diff(color_bounds)
    #color_values = steps[:-1]
    color_values = color_bounds[:-1] + diffs/2
    tick_formatter = mpl.ticker.FormatStrFormatter('%.0f')
    discrete_cmap = cmap.resampled(len(color_values))
    #sm = plt.cm.ScalarMappable(cmap=discrete_cmap, norm=norm)
    cb = plt.colorbar(
        scat,
        ax=mapax,
        location='left',
        anchor=(-0.5, 0.5),
        use_gridspec=True,
        shrink=1.01,
        pad=0.01,
        spacing='proportional',
        format=tick_formatter,
        boundaries=color_bounds,
        values=color_values
    )
    #cb.set_ticks(tick_values, labels=tick_formatter.format_ticks(tick_values))
    cb.ax.tick_params(labelsize='xx-small')
    cb.ax.set_ylabel('Response Time [yr]',fontsize='xx-small')
    cb.ax.minorticks_off()
    
    # gridlines
    label_style = {'fontsize': 'xx-small', 'rotation': 0}
    gl_maj = mapax.gridlines(
        draw_labels=['top', 'right'], linewidth=0.5, color='grey',
        alpha=0.4,
        linestyle=':',
        xlocs=mpl.ticker.MultipleLocator(20),
        ylocs=mpl.ticker.MultipleLocator(5),
        x_inline=False, y_inline=False,
        xlabel_style=label_style,
        ylabel_style=label_style,
        rotate_labels=False
    )
    gl_min = mapax.gridlines(
        draw_labels=False,
        linewidth=0.5,
        color='grey',
        alpha=0.25,
        linestyle=':',
        xlocs=mpl.ticker.MultipleLocator(10),
        ylocs=None,
    )
    mapax.set_title(plot_title, loc='center', fontsize='xx-small')
    
    plt.savefig(Path(f'{filename}.svg'))
    plt.savefig(Path(f'{filename}.png'), bbox_inches='tight')
